{"tid":864057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好意思系列] 港鐵3綫信號故障　林鄭月娥籲僱主體諒受影響僱員","createTime":"2018-10-16T03:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T03:07:50.000Z","uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3fec8f85f3e1f20c311fb697caba39ced91b61","tid":864057,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"港鐵在今早繁忙時間，3條綫出現信號故障，交通大受影響。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行政長官林鄭月娥表示，希望僱主體諒受影響的僱員</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，今早的事故是一個難以控制的場面，希望僱主體諒僱員。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，未了解港鐵今早故障的原因，但她促請港鐵要做好預防工作，亦要確保鐵路安全、可靠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423232-20181016.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423232-20181016.htm&d=5%2FstAs133giDQ%2FmLdZaAAYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=28700448\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423232-20181016.htm&h=5e670e18\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423232-20181016.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9ef4de38c7699f1eb9f77003efef3886a5572d50","tid":864057,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"就好似山竹之後個日咁"},{"pid":"ff7e25e89df84706515dae2f12d511066c0c5152","tid":864057,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"又互讓互諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e5af077b3c18e6d6dfa9227208641c3f30b611","tid":864057,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ef4de38c7699f1eb9f77003efef3886a5572d50","tid":864057,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"就好似山竹之後個日咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94a903b1c6ac8d097731ff51339d9c2aa4706e7","tid":864057,"u